權利以及其他更多權利[3]。人人有權不受歧視享受這些權利[3]。人權是最核心之自然權利，沒有人權，就沒有自由、平等、民主、憲政和博愛。<br />\n<br />\n人人都有腦，人地有追求，之後比政府打壓，點解要屌有追求既人？"},{"pid":"28b80bb01cc3a0080dfec8d2b5123f424b13e2f7","tid":2191301,"uid":4493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T11:37:05.000Z","msg":"重點係出咗去嘅唔會留言<br />\n所以日頭呢度係乜嘢人大家估到"},{"pid":"58796bf9de8b0b043d181aa016187632b473c097","tid":2191301,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b56e0b3b8dd64f314e67529590cc48ffd1847f0","tid":2191301,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"連登宜家已經俾大量五毛盤踞帶風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨立思考 相信自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T11:40:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>今日大成功</strong></span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdf75ee42ad371f58860b06fd23004c198258e8","tid":2191301,"uid":278168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"成功 = 達到原本目的<br />\n所以成唔成功視乎你覺得原本目的"},{"pid":"db1e6ff79d874ac728cd6734cebe0f2bb81bb8e8","tid":2191301,"uid":222392,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2b56e0b3b8dd64f314e67529590cc48ffd1847f0","tid":2191301,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"連登宜家已經俾大量五毛盤踞帶風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨立思考 相信自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"點成功呀？屌你老母臭閪！水鳩人出去俾狗濫捕叫成功呀？<br />\n你有緊張個手足咩？你有冇去跟進被捕人仕情況呀？<br />\n成你老母臭閪呀！"},{"pid":"3769f19e71be428a5e9265dcc50a09554f6ae305","tid":2191301,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T11:48:58.000Z","msg":"PR公司又冇咗一堆acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\"